on-with-nick-bordieri.html</a><br />\n5. 唔講Logic(E個係我好辛苦GE地方)，佢地成日咩都用聖經做指標(其實事上有好多惡人都用聖經做維穩，但如美國黑奴時其有人話obey to your earthly masters，就比人打都要)。一有好事發生就話係自己同神好，再認同自己做GE事係正確。(有因就有止果，但有止果唔等同有止因)。自己受到其他人批評就話係人地GE persecution。(冇錯，義人會受到persecution，但比人persecute GE 人，唔一定係義人)<br />\n6. 佢地有本叫&quot;First principle studies&quot;，信教GE人我好encourage 你地去睇下 <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=org.usd21.firstprinciples&amp;hl=en_US\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dorg.usd21.firstprinciples%26hl%3Den_US&d=mjxy7jgeiAJDqMaDnlkTCjM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=494fceab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=org.usd21.firstprinciples&amp;hl=en_US</a><br />\n<br />\n一個信仰如果係比人迫信/自己用理據去信服自己就唔係信仰，而係無知。所以係我重新認識信仰前我會不停進修哲學，邏輯學。總之，大家小心間教會。"},{"pid":"8999480ae36faf5abf8652fd902ee5a73a25e4ca","tid":926758,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T16:29:41.000Z","msg":"我想去A到睇下, 有冇?<br />\n同埋GE persecution, GE地方嘅GE 係指乜?"},{"pid":"76fe6d72b315df1ad2af3a76469af17f14f27c84","tid":926758,"uid":13986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8999480ae36faf5abf8652fd902ee5a73a25e4ca","tid":926758,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T16:29:41.000Z","msg":"我想去A到睇下, 有冇?<br />\n同埋GE persecution, GE地方嘅GE 係指乜?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T16:34:30.000Z","msg":"樓主文盲唔識字。<br />\n<br />\n嘅"},{"pid":"550684d1d1b7fbc6f45c874aa7e4a2fdca54014b","tid":926758,"uid":131356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76fe6d72b315df1ad2af3a76469af17f14f27c84","tid":926758,"uid":13986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8999480ae36faf5abf8652fd902ee5a73a25e4ca","tid":926758,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T16:29:41.000Z","msg":"我想去A到睇下, 有冇?<br />\n同埋GE persecution, GE地方嘅GE 係指乜?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T16:34:30.000Z","msg":"樓主文盲唔識字。<br />\